    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large panels, frames, or other assemblies on which are mounted switches, fuses, instruments, and protective devices; for smaller panels containing switches and fuses or circuit breakers, use "panelboards."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para grandes paneles, marcos, u otros ensamblajes en los cuales son montados interruptores, fusibles, instrumentos, y elementos de protección; para pequeños paneles que contienen interruptores y fusibles o interruptores de circuitos, usar "tablero de control."
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor grote panelen, kaders of andere assemblages waarop schakelaars, zekeringen, instrumenten en beschermende apparaten zijn bevestigd.  Voor kleine panelen die schakelaars, zekeringen en stroomonderbrekers bevatten wordt 'bedieningspanelen' gebruikt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Große Platte, Rahmen oder andere Anlage, auf denen Schalter, Sicherungen, Instrumente und Schutzeinrichtungen befestigt sind; für eine kleinere Platte mit Schaltern und Sicherungen oder Schutzschaltern, siehe "Verteiler (elektrische Systemkomponente)".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
